IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. REDREFM.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 BASE-REC.
    05 BASE-TEXT PIC X(5) VALUE "ABCDE".
01 LINEAR REDEFINES BASE-REC PIC X(5).
01 IDX PIC 9(1) VALUE 3.
01 CELL PIC X(1).
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN-PARA.
    MOVE LINEAR(IDX:1) TO CELL
    MOVE "." TO LINEAR(2:1)
    DISPLAY CELL
    DISPLAY LINEAR
    STOP RUN.
